ANTHONY'S RC CHURCH, NORTHVALE, NJ. THE FAMILY WILL RECEIVE FRIENDS SUNDAY 3, 6PM AND MONDAY 2, 4 AND 7, 9PM AT PIZZI FUNERAL HOME, 120 PARIS AVENUE, NORTHVALE, NJ (201, 767, 3050). IN LIEU OF FLOWERS, PLEASE DONATE TO THE CHARITY OF YOUR CHOICE, OR RAISE A GLASS TO VINCE. 1
